snippet.title: Hilarious dogs will make you burst into laughter - Funny dog compilation
snippet.description:
Dogs are amazing, and also very funny! Just look how all these dogs and puppies play, sleep, get along with cats, babies, how they fail, react to mirrors, make funny sounds,... So funny, ridiculous and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
